INSERT INTO `chat_history` VALUES (391758088987852800,'制作前端知识学习单页应用，采用卡片式布局展示HTML、CSS、JavaScript的示例和说明，包含代码高亮和实时预览功能。','user',391758088325152768,390705603766513664,'2026-03-18 14:07:46','2026-03-18 14:07:46',0),(391758269942710272,'\n\n# 代码生成 Agent 启动中...\n\n**应用ID:** 391758088325152768\n\n**生成类型:** single_html\n\n**原始需求:** 制作前端知识学习单页应用，采用卡片式布局展示HTML、CSS、JavaScript的示例和说明，包含代码高亮和实时预览功能。\n\n\n\n## 🎬 开始执行规划节点\n\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 工作流初始化\n\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 网络资源整理已完成\n\n- 整理网络资源: 1 字符\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 图片收集已完成\n\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 提示词增强已完成\n\n- 提示词已增强 (长度: 244 字符)\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 代码生成类型策略已完成\n\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: AI 代码生成已完成\n\n- 代码输出目录: E:\\AAA_idea_java\\RichCodeWeaver/appCode/code_output/single_html_391758088325152768\n\n**等待 AI 代码审查...**\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 代码审查\n\n- 审查结果: ✅ 通过\n\n\n### ✅ 执行步骤: 代码审查\n\n\n\n# 🎉 代码生成任务全部完成！\n\n','ai',391758088325152768,390705603766513664,'2026-03-18 14:08:30','2026-03-18 14:08:30',0),(391839727122145280,'创建一个现代风格计算器页面，支持基础数学运算和科学计算功能，包含清晰的按钮布局和实时结果。显示区域，支持明暗主题切换。','user',391839724840443904,390705603766513664,'2026-03-18 19:32:10','2026-03-18 19:32:10',0),(391840191884582912,'\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_START -->\n\n# 🚀 代码生成 Agent 启动\n\n<div class=\'workflow-meta\'>\n\n| 项目 | 信息 |\n|------|------|\n| 应用ID | `391839724840443904` |\n| 生成类型 | **single_html** |\n| 执行模式 | **分布式工作流** |\n| 原始需求 | 创建一个现代风格计算器页面，支持基础数学运算和科学计算功能，包含清晰的按钮布局和实时结果。显示区域，支持明暗主题切换。 |\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_EXECUTION_START -->\n\n## 📋 工作流执行计划\n\n<div class=\'workflow-steps\'>\n\n**执行阶段:**\n\n1. 🌐 网络资源整理\n2. 🖼️ 图片资源收集\n3. ✨ 提示词智能增强\n4. 🎯 代码类型策略分析\n5. 💻 AI 代码生成\n6. 🔍 代码质量审查\n7. 🏗️ 项目构建部署\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:__START__ -->\n\n### ✅ 工作流初始化\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**⚙️ 工作流初始化**\n\n- ✓ 工作流上下文已创建\n- ✓ 执行参数已配置完成\n- ✓ 准备开始执行各节点任务\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:__START__ -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:web_resource_organizer -->\n\n### ✅ 网络资源整理已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🌐 网络资源整理节点**\n\n- ✓ 整理完成：收集到 **1209** 字符的网络资源\n- ✓ 资源类型：文本素材、URL链接等\n- ✓ 状态：已整合到工作流上下文\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:web_resource_organizer -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:image_collector -->\n\n### ✅ 图片收集已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🖼️ 图片资源收集节点**\n\n- ℹ️ 未找到相关图片资源或无需收集\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:image_collector -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:prompt_enhancer -->\n\n### ✅ 提示词增强已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**✨ 提示词增强节点**\n\n- ✓ 增强完成：提示词优化至 **1609** 字符\n- ✓ 增强内容：融合网络资源、图片信息\n- ✓ 质量提升：更精准的代码生成指令\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:prompt_enhancer -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:ai_code_generator_type_strategy -->\n\n### ✅ 代码生成类型策略已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🎯 代码类型策略节点**\n\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:ai_code_generator_type_strategy -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:code_generator -->\n\n### ✅ AI 代码生成已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**💻 AI 代码生成节点**\n\n- ✓ 生成完成：代码已输出\n- ✓ 输出路径：`E:\\AAA_idea_java\\RichCodeWeaver/appCode/code_output/single_html_391839724840443904`\n- ✓ 下一步：等待 AI 代码质量审查\n\n> 🔍 正在启动代码审查流程...\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:code_generator -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:ai_code_reviewer -->\n\n### ✅ 代码审查\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🔍 代码审查节点**\n\n- ✅ **审查通过**：代码质量符合标准\n- ✓ 代码规范：符合最佳实践\n- ✓ 功能完整：满足需求描述\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:ai_code_reviewer -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:__END__ -->\n\n### ✅ 代码审查\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**⚙️ 工作流初始化**\n\n- ✓ 工作流上下文已创建\n- ✓ 执行参数已配置完成\n- ✓ 准备开始执行各节点任务\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:__END__ -->\n\n\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_COMPLETE -->\n\n---\n\n# 🎉 代码生成任务完成\n\n<div class=\'workflow-summary\'>\n\n**✅ 所有工作流节点执行完毕**\n\n- 🌐 网络资源已整理\n- 🖼️ 图片资源已收集\n- ✨ 提示词已增强\n- 🎯 代码类型已确定\n- 💻 代码已生成\n- 🔍 质量已审查\n- 🏗️ 项目已构建\n\n**下一步操作：**\n\n- 📱 切换到「应用模式」查看预览\n- 🚀 点击「部署」发布到线上\n- 💾 点击「下载」获取源代码\n\n</div>\n\n','ai',391839724840443904,390705603766513664,'2026-03-18 19:34:01','2026-03-18 19:34:01',0),(392814354946338816,'为一位个体互联网/IT从业者打造一个纯静态的开发者工具箱网站，采用 GitHub 风格配色（背景 #fff，文字与边框 #24292e），整体布局基于标签页切换导航，支持平滑过渡动效。网站包含以下五个真实可用的前端工具，均以独立卡片形式呈现，且全部功能在浏览器端完成（无需后端）：\n\n1. **JSON 格式化工具**：支持 JSON 字符串的格式化（美化）与压缩（最小化），实时校验语法并高亮错误；\n2. **Base64 编解码工具**：支持文本 ↔ Base64 的双向编解码，兼容 UTF-8 编码，输入变化时实时输出结果；\n3. **时间戳转换工具**：支持 Unix 时间戳（秒/毫秒）与标准日期时间（ISO 8601、YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS 等常见格式）互转，可手动输入或点击“当前时间”快速填充；\n4. **正则表达式测试工具**：提供模式输入、测试字符串输入、标志选项（g/i/m）、匹配结果高亮显示及捕获组解析，支持实时匹配反馈；\n5. **颜色选择器工具**：纯前端实现的 HEX / RGB / HSL 三格式实时互转，含色块预览、复制颜色值功能，支持键盘输入与拾色交互（如 input[type=\"color\"] 基础增强）。\n\n所有工具均具备输入区与输出区的实时双向预览能力，标签页切换时有淡入/滑动等轻量动效，整体界面响应式设计，适配桌面与移动端浏览。数据处理全程运行于浏览器，不依赖任何外部 API 或服务端逻辑。','user',392814353788710912,390705603766513664,'2026-03-21 12:05:00','2026-03-21 12:05:00',0),(392814512463425536,'```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>开发者工具箱</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --bg-color: #fff;\n            --text-color: #24292e;\n            --accent-color: #0366d6;\n            --border-color: #d0d7de;\n            --hover-color: #f1f1f1;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav button {\n            background: none;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            padding: 8px 12px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav button:hover {\n            background: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        nav button.active {\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        main {\n            display: none;\n        }\n\n        main.active {\n            display: block;\n            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeIn {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        .tool-card {\n            background: #f6f8fa;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .tool-card:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.02);\n        }\n\n        .tool-card h2 {\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .input-output {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 10px;\n        }\n\n        textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            min-height: 100px;\n            padding: 10px;\n            font-family: monospace;\n            font-size: 14px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            resize: vertical;\n            outline: none;\n        }\n\n        .output {\n            background: #eef0f2;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            white-space: pre-wrap;\n            word-break: break-all;\n        }\n\n        .error {\n            color: red;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .buttons button {\n            padding: 8px 12px;\n            border: none;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            color: white;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .buttons button:hover {\n            background: #005bb5;\n        }\n\n        .time-buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .color-picker {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 10px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .color-preview {\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 40px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .copy-button {\n            padding: 6px 10px;\n            border: none;\n            background: var(--accent-color);\n            color: white;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n        }\n\n        .copy-button:hover {\n            background: #005bb5;\n        }\n\n        /* 响应式设计 */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            nav {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 5px;\n            }\n\n            .tool-card {\n                padding: 15px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            header {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                gap: 10px;\n            }\n\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 20px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>开发者工具箱</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <button class=\"tab-button active\" data-tab=\"json\">JSON 格式化</button>\n            <button class=\"tab-button\" data-tab=\"base64\">Base64 编解码</button>\n            <button class=\"tab-button\" data-tab=\"timestamp\">时间戳转换</button>\n            <button class=\"tab-button\" data-tab=\"regex\">正则表达式测试</button>\n            <button class=\"tab-button\" data-tab=\"color\">颜色选择器</button>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <main id=\"json\" class=\"tool-card active\">\n        <h2>JSON 格式化工具</h2>\n        <div class=\"input-output\">\n            <textarea id=\"json-input\" placeholder=\"输入 JSON 字符串\"></textarea>\n            <div class=\"output\" id=\"json-output\"></div>\n            <div class=\"buttons\">\n                <button onclick=\"formatJson()\">格式化</button>\n                <button onclick=\"minifyJson()\">压缩</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <main id=\"base64\" class=\"tool-card\">\n        <h2>Base64 编解码工具</h2>\n        <div class=\"input-output\">\n            <textarea id=\"base64-input\" placeholder=\"输入文本或 Base64 字符串\"></textarea>\n            <div class=\"output\" id=\"base64-output\"></div>\n            <div class=\"buttons\">\n                <button onclick=\"encodeBase64()\">编码</button>\n                <button onclick=\"decodeBase64()\">解码</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <main id=\"timestamp\" class=\"tool-card\">\n        <h2>时间戳转换工具</h2>\n        <div class=\"input-output\">\n            <input type=\"number\" id=\"timestamp-input\" placeholder=\"输入时间戳（秒/毫秒）\">\n            <div class=\"output\" id=\"timestamp-output\"></div>\n            <div class=\"time-buttons\">\n                <button onclick=\"getCurrentTime()\">当前时间</button>\n                <button onclick=\"convertTimestamp()\">转换</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <main id=\"regex\" class=\"tool-card\">\n        <h2>正则表达式测试工具</h2>\n        <div class=\"input-output\">\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"regex-pattern\" placeholder=\"输入正则表达式\">\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"regex-string\" placeholder=\"输入测试字符串\">\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"regex-flags\" placeholder=\"输入标志（g/i/m）\">\n            <div class=\"output\" id=\"regex-output\"></div>\n            <div class=\"buttons\">\n                <button onclick=\"testRegex()\">测试</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <main id=\"color\" class=\"tool-card\">\n        <h2>颜色选择器工具</h2>\n        <div class=\"input-output\">\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"color-input\" placeholder=\"输入 HEX / RGB / HSL\">\n            <div class=\"color-preview\" id=\"color-preview\"></div>\n            <div class=\"output\" id=\"color-output\"></div>\n            <div class=\"buttons\">\n                <button onclick=\"copyColor()\">复制颜色值</button>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"color-picker\">\n                <input type=\"color\" id=\"color-picker\" onchange=\"updateColorPicker()\">\n                <span id=\"color-code\"></span>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </main>\n\n    <script>\n        // 标签页切换逻辑\n        const tabs = document.querySelectorAll(\'.tab-button\');\n        const contents = document.querySelectorAll(\'main\');\n\n        tabs.forEach(tab => {\n            tab.addEventListener(\'click\', () => {\n                tabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove(\'active\'));\n                contents.forEach(c => c.classList.remove(\'active\'));\n\n                tab.classList.add(\'active\');\n                document.getElementById(tab.dataset.tab).classList.add(\'active\');\n            });\n        });\n\n        // JSON 格式化工具\n        function formatJson() {\n            const input = document.getElementById(\'json-input\').value;\n            try {\n                const parsed = JSON.parse(input);\n                document.getElementById(\'json-output\').textContent = JSON.stringify(parsed, null, 2);\n            } catch (e) {\n                document.getElementById(\'json-output\').textContent = `错误: ${e.message}`;\n            }\n        }\n\n        function minifyJson() {\n            const input = document.getElementById(\'json-input\').value;\n            try {\n                const parsed = JSON.parse(input);\n                document.getElementById(\'json-output\').textContent = JSON.stringify(parsed);\n            } catch (e) {\n                document.getElementById(\'json-output\').textContent = `错误: ${e.message}`;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Base64 编解码工具\n        function encodeBase64() {\n            const input = document.getElementById(\'base64-input\').value;\n            document.getElementById(\'base64-output\').textContent = btoa(input);\n        }\n\n        function decodeBase64() {\n            const input = document.getElementById(\'base64-input\').value;\n            try {\n                document.getElementById(\'base64-output\').textContent = atob(input);\n            } catch (e) {\n                document.getElementById(\'base64-output\').textContent = `错误: ${e.message}`;\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 时间戳转换工具\n        function getCurrentTime() {\n            const now = new Date();\n            document.getElementById(\'timestamp-input\').value = Math.floor(now.getTime() / 1000);\n        }\n\n        function convertTimestamp() {\n            const input = document.getElementById(\'timestamp-input\').value;\n            const isMillisecond = input.length > 10; // 判断是否为毫秒时间戳\n            const timestamp = parseInt(input);\n            if (!isNaN(timestamp)) {\n                const date = new Date(timestamp * (isMillisecond ? 1 : 1000));\n                const isoDate = date.toISOString().replace(\'T\', \' \').substring(0, 19);\n                const formattedDate = date.toLocaleString();\n                document.getElementById(\'timestamp-output\').textContent = `ISO 8601: ${isoDate}\\n本地时间: ${formattedDate}`;\n            } else {\n                document.getElementById(\'timestamp-output\').textContent = \'无效的时间戳\';\n            }\n        }\n\n        // 正则表达式测试工具\n        function testRegex() {\n            const pattern = document.getElementById(\'regex-pattern\').value;\n            const string = document.getElementById(\'regex-string\').value;\n            const flags = document.getElementById(\'regex-flags\').value;\n            const regex = new RegExp(pattern, flags);\n            const matches = string.match(regex);\n            let output = \'\';\n            if (matches) {\n                output += `匹配结果: ${matches.join(\', \')}`;\n                if (regex.global && matches.length > 1) {\n                    output += `\\n捕获组: ${matches[1] || \'无\'}`;\n                }\n            } else {\n                output = \'未找到匹配项\';\n            }\n            document.getElementById(\'regex-output\').textContent = output;\n        }\n\n        // 颜色选择器工具\n        function updateColorPicker() {\n            const picker = document.getElementById(\'color-picker\');\n            const code = document.getElementById(\'color-code\');\n            const preview = document.getElementById(\'color-preview\');\n            const value = picker.value;\n            preview.style.backgroundColor = value;\n            code.textContent = value;\n            document.getElementById(\'color-input\').value = value;\n        }\n\n        function copyColor() {\n            const code = document.getElementById(\'color-code\').textContent;\n            navigator.clipboard.writeText(code).then(() => {\n                alert(\'颜色值已复制到剪贴板\');\n            });\n        }\n\n        // 监听颜色输入框变化\n        document.getElementById(\'color-input\').addEventListener(\'input\', () => {\n            const input = document.getElementById(\'color-input\').value;\n            const preview = document.getElementById(\'color-preview\');\n            const code = document.getElementById(\'color-code\');\n            try {\n                // 尝试解析 HEX、RGB 或 HSL\n                if (/^#([A-Fa-f0-9]{6}|[A-Fa-f0-9]{3})$/.test(input)) {\n                    preview.style.backgroundColor = input;\n                    code.textContent = input;\n                } else if (/^rgb\\(\\s*\\d+\\s*,\\s*\\d+\\s*,\\s*\\d+\\s*\\)$/.test(input)) {\n                    preview.style.backgroundColor = input;\n                    code.textContent = input;\n                } else if (/^hsl\\(\\s*\\d+\\s*,\\s*\\d+%\\s*,\\s*\\d+%\\s*\\)$/.test(input)) {\n                    preview.style.backgroundColor = input;\n                    code.textContent = input;\n                } else {\n                    code.textContent = \'无效的颜色格式\';\n                }\n            } catch (e) {\n                code.textContent = \'无效的颜色格式\';\n            }\n        });\n\n        // 初始化颜色预览\n        updateColorPicker();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```','ai',392814353788710912,390705603766513664,'2026-03-21 12:05:37','2026-03-21 12:05:37',0),(392815273918345216,'创建一个简单的日历小工具','user',392815273259839488,390705603766513664,'2026-03-21 12:08:39','2026-03-21 12:08:39',0),(392815340951711744,'```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <title>简单日历小工具</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4a90e2;\n            --secondary-color: #f5f7fa;\n            --text-color: #333;\n            --background-color: #fff;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: \"Microsoft YaHei\", sans-serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: flex-start;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-container {\n            width: 100%;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-header {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-header h2 {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-header button {\n            background: none;\n            border: none;\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .calendar-weekdays {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-weekdays div {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-days {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);\n            gap: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-day {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 40px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-day.today {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .calendar-day:hover {\n            background-color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .calendar-header h2 {\n                font-size: 1.2rem;\n            }\n\n            .calendar-day {\n                height: 30px;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"calendar-container\">\n        <div class=\"calendar-header\">\n            <button id=\"prevMonth\">❮</button>\n            <h2 id=\"currentMonthYear\"></h2>\n            <button id=\"nextMonth\">❯</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"calendar-weekdays\">\n            <div>日</div>\n            <div>一</div>\n            <div>二</div>\n            <div>三</div>\n            <div>四</div>\n            <div>五</div>\n            <div>六</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"calendar-days\" id=\"calendarDays\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        const calendarDays = document.getElementById(\'calendarDays\');\n        const currentMonthYear = document.getElementById(\'currentMonthYear\');\n        const prevMonthBtn = document.getElementById(\'prevMonth\');\n        const nextMonthBtn = document.getElementById(\'nextMonth\');\n\n        let currentDate = new Date();\n\n        function renderCalendar() {\n            const year = currentDate.getFullYear();\n            const month = currentDate.getMonth();\n\n            const firstDay = new Date(year, month, 1);\n            const lastDay = new Date(year, month + 1, 0);\n\n            const daysInMonth = lastDay.getDate();\n            const startDay = firstDay.getDay();\n\n            // 清空之前的日期\n            calendarDays.innerHTML = \'\';\n\n            // 填充空白的日期（前一个月）\n            for (let i = 0; i < startDay; i++) {\n                const dayDiv = document.createElement(\'div\');\n                dayDiv.classList.add(\'calendar-day\');\n                calendarDays.appendChild(dayDiv);\n            }\n\n            // 填充当前月的日期\n            for (let day = 1; day <= daysInMonth; day++) {\n                const dayDiv = document.createElement(\'div\');\n                dayDiv.classList.add(\'calendar-day\');\n                dayDiv.textContent = day;\n\n                // 判断是否是今天\n                const today = new Date();\n                if (year === today.getFullYear() && month === today.getMonth() && day === today.getDate()) {\n                    dayDiv.classList.add(\'today\');\n                }\n\n                calendarDays.appendChild(dayDiv);\n            }\n\n            // 更新月份和年份标题\n            const monthNames = [\n                \'一月\', \'二月\', \'三月\', \'四月\', \'五月\', \'六月\',\n                \'七月\', \'八月\', \'九月\', \'十月\', \'十一月\', \'十二月\'\n            ];\n            currentMonthYear.textContent = `${monthNames[month]} ${year}`;\n        }\n\n        prevMonthBtn.addEventListener(\'click\', () => {\n            currentDate.setMonth(currentDate.getMonth() - 1);\n            renderCalendar();\n        });\n\n        nextMonthBtn.addEventListener(\'click\', () => {\n            currentDate.setMonth(currentDate.getMonth() + 1);\n            renderCalendar();\n        });\n\n        // 初始化渲染\n        renderCalendar();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```','ai',392815273259839488,390705603766513664,'2026-03-21 12:08:55','2026-03-21 12:08:55',0),(392817207752646656,'创建一个简单的日历小工具','user',392817205487722496,390705603766513664,'2026-03-21 12:16:20','2026-03-21 13:40:41',1),(392817475802226688,'\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_START -->\n\n# 🚀 代码生成 Agent 启动\n\n<div class=\'workflow-meta\'>\n\n| 项目 | 信息 |\n|------|------|\n| 应用ID | `392817205487722496` |\n| 生成类型 | **single_html** |\n| 执行模式 | **分布式工作流** |\n| 原始需求 | 创建一个简单的日历小工具 |\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_EXECUTION_START -->\n\n## 📋 工作流执行计划\n\n<div class=\'workflow-steps\'>\n\n**执行阶段:**\n\n1. 🌐 网络资源整理\n2. 🖼️ 图片资源收集\n3. ✨ 提示词智能增强\n4. 🎯 代码类型策略分析\n5. 💻 AI 代码生成\n6. 🔍 代码质量审查\n7. 🏗️ 项目构建部署\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:__START__ -->\n\n### ✅ 工作流初始化\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**⚙️ 工作流初始化**\n\n- ✓ 工作流上下文已创建\n- ✓ 执行参数已配置完成\n- ✓ 准备开始执行各节点任务\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:__START__ -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:web_resource_organizer -->\n\n### ✅ 网络资源整理已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🌐 网络资源整理节点**\n\n- ✓ 整理完成：收集到 **1** 字符的网络资源\n- ✓ 资源类型：文本素材、URL链接等\n- ✓ 状态：已整合到工作流上下文\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:web_resource_organizer -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:image_collector -->\n\n### ✅ 图片收集已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🖼️ 图片资源收集节点**\n\n- ℹ️ 未找到相关图片资源或无需收集\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:image_collector -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:prompt_enhancer -->\n\n### ✅ 提示词增强已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**✨ 提示词增强节点**\n\n- ✓ 增强完成：提示词优化至 **112** 字符\n- ✓ 增强内容：融合网络资源、图片信息\n- ✓ 质量提升：更精准的代码生成指令\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:prompt_enhancer -->\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" /